TaxAct is an American tax preparation software provider and subsidiary of Blucora. It is a member of the Free File Alliance, a free federal tax preparation and electronic filing program for eligible individual taxpayers developed through a partnership between the IRS and a group of private sector tax software companies. 
TaxAct is a leading provider of affordable digital and download tax software for individuals, business owners and tax professionals. TaxAct offers a 100% accuracy guarantee on tax returns, and provides unlimited access to certified public accountants and technology support professionals to answer any customer questions. The companyâ€™s strong commitment to transparency is further demonstrated by its unique Price Lock Guarantee, which ensures that users pay the listed price for their software at the time they start on their returns, regardless of when they file them. All forms are IRS and State approved.


